snippet.title: Sandboxels Educational Lab Examples - Sodium Reaction, Density, Boiling
snippet.description:
Educators can use this browser-based program to run science labs with their students. Sandboxels has hundreds of elements (materials, fluids, plants, animals, etc.) with countless interactions between them.

Anyone can try it on the website: https://sandboxels.R74n.com

Simply provide students with the link and instruct them, or let them experiment and see the effects of their actions.
